  <!-- <logo>http://maven.apache.org/images/maven.jpg</logo> -->
    <description>This project's goal is to provide an application for managing 
        all your household issues. Currently, it is able to keep a list of food 
        which is on hand. You can specify expiry dates and sort your food after 
        them so you always have an overview of what is going to seed soon.
        </description>
  
  <!-- a short description of what the project does -->
    <shortDescription>An application for keeping track 
        of food in a household.</shortDescription>

